    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[S. T.] In nomine domini Dei et salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi, Otto divina
                        ordinante providencia inperator agustus et item Otto filio eius gratia Dei
                        regis, anno regni eius Deo propicio hic in Italia anno secundo, die tercio
                        kalendas iulio, indictione sexta. Constat nos <persName
                            key="#Roman #siblingOf"><name ref="Milius">Milio</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Roman #siblingOf"><name ref="Ermericus"
                            >Emericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germanis</rs> filiis quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ghisi">Gisoni</name></persName> habitatoris in loco qui dicitur
                            <placeName>S. Vigilio</placeName>, qui professi sumus ex nacione nostra
                        lege vivimus <rs key="#Roman">Romana</rs>, vindimus a presenti die tradamus
                        tibi <persName ref="#people/4819">Gisani</persName> filius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Leo">Leoni</name></persName> abitatrice in S.
                        Vigilio, id sunt in integru inter casis et omnibus rebus illis iuris nostris
                        quam abere et possidere visi sumus tam in prato <placeName><geogName
                                ref="#estates/4303"
                                key="#Houses #Petiae #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                >Matoli</geogName></placeName> et in
                        <placeName><geogName
                                ref="#estates/4304"
                                key="#Houses #Petiae #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                >Roveretolo</geogName></placeName> in <placeName><geogName
                                        ref="#estates/4305"
                                        key="#Houses #Petiae #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                        >Motelena</geogName></placeName>
                        adque in <placeName><geogName
                                ref="#estates/4306"
                                key="#Houses #Petiae #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                >Gurgo Kanzoli</geogName></placeName> seu in
                        <placeName><geogName
                                ref="#estates/4307"
                                key="#Houses #Petiae #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                >Lavatura</geogName></placeName> adque in <placeName><geogName
                                        ref="#estates/4308"
                                        key="#Houses #Petiae #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                        >Mamurre</geogName></placeName>
                        tam <rs key="#Houses">casalivoras</rs> seu reliquis <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, insolis, usum aquarum, <rs key="#Canals"
                            >accessiones</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">flumenis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fountains">fontaneis</rs>, omnia et ex omnibus iamdictis casis et
                        rebus; et sunt ipsas res per mensura et racionem ad <rs key="#Size">pertica
                            legiptima de pedis duodecim</rs> mensurata in prenominatis locis prato
                        Matoli et in Roveretolo in Motelena et in Gurgo Kanzoli seu in Lavatura
                        adque in Mamurre, sunt inter casalivoras et vineis seu pratis adque terris
                        arabilis iuges viginti, si amplius de ipsas res habueritis aut inventum
                        fueritis, per ipsam cartulam abeatis totam in integrum tibi cui supra Gisani
                        per testus istius cartula vindicionis a presenti die confirmamus ad abendum,
                        tenendum, posidendum et faciendum exinde iamdictis casis et res tam tu Gisa
                        vel tuis heredes aut cui vos dederitis, quit aut qualiter volueritis iure
                        proprietario nomine, sine ullius contradictione; et recepimus nos pro
                        suprascriptis germanis pro suprascriptas res una cum omnia superioribus et
                        inferioribus suis, ad te cui supra Gisa per <rs key="#Missus">misso</rs> tuo
                            <persName key="#Missus"><name ref="Azo">Azo</name></persName> in specie
                        valente <rs key="#Price">solidos duodecim</rs> fenitum precium; unde
                        expomdimus adque promittimus nos suprascriptis germanis vel nostris heredes
                        tibi cui supra Gisani vel ad tuis heredibus suprascriptas res ab homne
                        homine defensare, et si defensare non potuerimus, aut contra hanc cartula
                        ire quandoque agere presumserimus, tun componamus vos predictas res<rs
                            key="#Penalty"> in dublo</rs>, sicut diebus illis melioratas fuerit sub
                        extimacione in consimilibus locis, et omnis nos vel heredum et parentum
                        nostrorum repeticione cessantes; et nec nobis licead umquam ullo tempore de
                        hoc factum aliter nisi quod ad me semel ex factum vel traditum sub
                        iusiurandum me inviolabiliter conservare promittimus cum stipulacione
                        subnixa. Actum <placeName ref="#places/191">Regio</placeName> feliciter.
                        Signa manibus Milii et Amelricus germanis qui hanc cartula vindicionis fieri
                        et firmare rogavi. Signa manibus <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName> seu <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Gampertus">Gamperti</name></persName> homini
                        Romani de civitate Regio, rogatis <rs key="#Witness">testis</rs>. Signa
                        manibus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Liutius"
                            >Liuzoni</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Clemens">Clementi</name></persName> seu <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Leo">Leoni</name></persName> adque <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petroni</name></persName> de
                        suprascripta civitate Regio, rogatis testis. [S. T.] Scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Judge"><name ref="Teutius">Teuzo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> domni
                        inperatori hac regi postradita complevi et dedit.</ab>
                </div>
